In re Resignation of Luginbuhl.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Luginbuhl (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 93-1024 Submitted June 1, 1993 Decided June 2, 1993.)

The resignation of Randall Jay Luginbuhl of Columbus, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0022841, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
